</taxonomicName>
is known only from the Atlantic Forest of 
<collectingCountry id="89BB76169704E36CF54BFD67023E043F" box="[1064,1136,764,789]" name="Brazil" pageId="7" pageNumber="238">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="B9B6650D9704E36CF1A4FC8402C7041D" box="[199,1161,799,824]" pageId="7" pageNumber="238" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="F11336869704E36CF1A4FC8402C7041D" blockId="7.[151,1437,151,824]" box="[199,1161,799,824]" pageId="7" pageNumber="238">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA949704E36CF1A4FC8407000412" bold="true" box="[199,334,799,824]" pageId="7" pageNumber="238">Etymology.</emphasis>
